.\" Man page for lmm game
.TH LMM-GAME 1 "2026-01-29" "lmm" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lmm game \- Game management commands
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lmm game
\fISUBCOMMAND\fR [\fIARGS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage game configuration and default game selection.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
.B set-default \fIGAME_ID\fR
Set the default game so \fB--game\fR is not needed for every command.
.TP
.B show-default
Show the current default game.
.TP
.B clear-default
Clear the default game.
.TP
.B detect
Scan Steam libraries for known moddable games and optionally add them to
\fIgames.yaml\fR. Prompts for which games to add (e.g. 1,2 or all or none).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lmm (1),
.BR lmm-status (1).
